# Technology Stack

This project uses the following technologies:

## Core
- Flutter SDK for cross-platform development
- Dart programming language

## State Management
- Riverpod or Provider for state management
- Repository pattern for data access

## Navigation
- GoRouter for declarative routing

## Data Handling
- Dio for network requests
- Hive or SharedPreferences for local storage
- JSON serialization for data models

## UI Components
- Material Design 3 with custom theme
- CachedNetworkImage for image handling
- Custom animations for enhanced UX

When implementing features, use these technologies consistently throughout the project.